Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============TEXT ============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直都想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 如此激动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神好像在问我为什么要出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你好像过的很愉快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会出现在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当愉快这种感情将你内心动摇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最不想见的人就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:01:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么不想见我吗 优库里伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是我的上司把和路塞伊斯大人掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我接到了杀死和路塞伊斯大人的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么塞拉会接到杀死优的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉的目的不是把优带回忍者村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成杀死优啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}你恨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我当时还那么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为两个人可以就那样一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法原谅杀死7th abyss的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才对我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「消失吧」这样冷酷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很遗憾 当时我确实消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并非是从世上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6\fad(16,166)}你的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方很让我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过更让我吃惊的是你竟然还交上了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 要说我的愿望的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以会下暗杀指令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我的组织认为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅加洛来袭是和路塞伊斯大人的魔力所导致的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉菲姆 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊 这种指令肯定无效的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说的这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你要杀死优吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题你不问就不知道答案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那答案不是很清楚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我自己去找和路塞伊斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下 你们这些吸血忍者怎么都这么死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想做的事情不做就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不懂「任务」的分量有多重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能违反规定 所以我才要成为你的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优的生命没有任务重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种说法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们吸血忍者来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话我已经听腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要杀死优吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫你不要问些明摆着的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是想杀她还是不想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有问吸血忍者 而是在问塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会想杀死她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧 步和耍叶子的都别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去找死灵师不是更重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是很坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用奉承我 真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也全靠你我想明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要找到优啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 不要连目标都没有就乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 看的正起劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜托你 优库里伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有你能实现我的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要来看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像都在拼命找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看嘛 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你还继续把我的话当耳旁风…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西怎么会突然就倒下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 但脸好像被压坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来原本就是长这样子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只是稍微让你见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后可能就会发生更可怕的事情了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看 你又动摇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅加洛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 没有穿校服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死灵师的人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 快闪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥我会得宠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个河童是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄瓜除了生吃还可以煮着吃炒着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 我现在就把你拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点蛆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 还差一点 加油 春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}邪恶的我看到这里以为是在生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}别伤害春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它召唤过来的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是再明白不过了吗 优库里伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心一动摇就会招来灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是因为这样你才发誓不说话不动摇的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤来死亡之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 打扰你们说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你是玛蒂莱依斯魔法学校的老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你的传闻已经传到冥界了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 究竟是怎么样的传闻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你很强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便问下 你找我有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见我的学生被整成那样 我可不能坐视不理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}死灵战士大战怪物人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘剑·燕返
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…300%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,400 500 600
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你想干什么 友纪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄倒 弄倒后拉开它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 滚开 你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川 塞拉菲姆 把它推开 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这家伙太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 动呀 动呀 动呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动啊啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是玛蒂莱依斯魔法学校的大师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖了 没什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 友纪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么东西 刚才那束光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑住 梅尔·修德罗姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吸我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认母体异常 术式限制解除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才这下是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝乃生命之分歧点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一咏唱确认 术式解放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友纪 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾走向生路 汝去往死路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二咏唱确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬碎吧 Masticore
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终咏唱确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下那招可就连灰都不剩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 看来没带着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「没办法 就帮帮你们吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}和魔装少女咒语一样 玩倒句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mystletainn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话了 快变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘剑·燕返
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3Q 塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虽然我可爱又迷人 但我会招来死亡」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融化冻结的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一咏唱确认 解放术式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝将会把众神的气息化作暴风雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二咏唱确认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,absolute Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终咏唱确认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这就是京子所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的最强魔装兵器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可以算是我旧友的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:14:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想让相川收留她一阵子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}会停下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有解除装置喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是设定成自动关闭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦暴走 也有自爆的可能性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 如果出现了这种情况的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了这种情况的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能期望相川来解决问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈时也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是个了不起的魔法使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么了 为什么那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身后那个玩意很怪异吧 很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步 为什么要阻止我 这么下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出手 对手可是友纪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天和我们疯玩了一整天的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:15:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 忍者无论何时都该不惧危险上前战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你会那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里能交给我来处理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了 可是如果你失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就用剑把你插成刺猬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没辙了 步 你可要想办法摆平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友纪 你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认不出我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认母体异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离自爆装置启动之前 还剩30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别进来 别进入我的内心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着 等着我 友纪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然连你都会被一起炸飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}10…9…8…7…6
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这种事发生啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开 叫你走开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会爆炸喔 没必要连你也一起陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开 快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 快离开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不离开 我绝对不离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友纪（yuki）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡回一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 友纪（tomonori）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你妹的tomonori啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 和我说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可貌相 他相当有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优库里伍德 在你实现我的愿望之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我的话还没说完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}我戳 我戳 我戳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全煮熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一股焦味儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和路塞伊斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了啊 我们到处找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛 来 我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了 路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今 今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}你们先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗 我也陪你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 别回来的太晚了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上都是灰 我先回去烧洗澡水了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔大家一起玩玩也不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都怪我 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有我 今天就不会发生这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步和春奈还有塞拉 都对我施以温柔的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我很高兴 而我也毫不顾忌的接受了这份好意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我是无法和他人在一起的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来让你们受了不少苦 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我继续待在你们身边 总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又会害的某人伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤来死亡之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大到让这地区的人都能看到的大雪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望厨艺可以双倍增强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我的料理可以让这里的人们笑容常在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和步他们…永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}希望她们的愿望都不要实现  步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有我的愿望实现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会写下这种混账愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优库…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在烦恼个什么劲啊 僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 步 又不是生离死别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切才刚开始呢 黏黏的纳豆 步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种明摆着的事了 春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不是黏黏的纳豆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.86,0:22:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Never give up（永不放弃）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\a6}出去狩猎 不过恐怕反而会被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.63,0:24:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么叫political correctness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.88,0:24:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来就像paris collection一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说词语表达起来不带男女差别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.53,0:24:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是像空姐之类的词？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.90,0:24:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我和塞拉菲姆不称自己是女忍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.25,0:24:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也成为吸血忍者吧


